%F A381055 a(n) = (-1)^(n+1)*A006370(n).
%F A381055 a(n) = (1/4)*((-1)^(n+1)*(7*n+2)+5*n+2).
%F A381055 G.f.: x*(2*x^2-x+4)/((x-1)^2*(x+1)^2). - _Alois P. Heinz_, Aug 13 2025
%e A381055 a(0) = -0/2 = 0; a(1) = 3*1 + 1 = 4; a(10) = -10/2 = -5.
